  "dateModified": "2026-03-09",
  "datePublished": "2026-03-09",
  "description": "A virtual tabletop is a digital platform that reproduces key tabletop play aids online: maps, tokens, dice rollers, character sheets, handouts, and shared visual space. It does not replace the [tabletop role-playing game](../index.md) with a full video game. Instead, it provides virtual analogs of the tools a group would otherwise place on a physical table.",
